script = ExtResource("1_8rycr")
data = "So I guess this could be some type of tutorial/info for the player.

Most of the stuff works the way you'd expect it to work.
You can press RMB on an icon in the taskbar to close the app.
You can move the image in the image files using your mouse, and zoom using scroll."
